The first time we got there we missed the right turn and in a few seconds ended up looking at Colosseum :) Late evening and night walks are pleasant and pretty safe.	Restaurants were plenty in the area and we found the area safe to walk at night.	Quiet, cute, safe neighborhood - easy walk to Colosseum, Forum, and lots of other sites.	It could be a bit noisy - you're not completely safe from noise coming from neighbouring rooms and corridors - but at least the street is absolutelly quiet at night.